00:01:24.120 --> 00:01:27.597
Let me not be in delusion.

00:01:28.089 --> 00:01:31.594
Take me away from illusions.

00:01:31.714 --> 00:01:34.243
Keep me in reality.

00:01:34.363 --> 00:01:38.738
Take away the sheen of superficiality.

00:01:39.464 --> 00:01:43.391
Let me enjoy Your Feet in my heart.

00:01:43.511 --> 00:01:46.331
Let me see Your Feet in my heart.”
